7#include <unordered_map>
8#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect/AstHelpers.h"
9#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect/Debug.h"
10#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect/EnvironmentVariable.h"
11#include "compiler/translator/tree_ops/SimplifyLoopConditions.h"
12#include "compiler/translator/tree_util/IntermRebuild.h"
13#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect/FixTypeConstructors.h"
14using namespace sh;
15////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
16namespace
17{
18class FixTypeTraverser : public TIntermTraverser
19{
20public:
21 FixTypeTraverser() : TIntermTraverser(false, false, true) {}
22
23 bool visitAggregate(Visit visit, TIntermAggregate *aggregateNode) override
24 {
25 if (visit != Visit::PostVisit)
26 {
27 return true;
28 }
29 if (aggregateNode->isConstructor())
30 {
31 const TType &retType = aggregateNode->getType();
32 if (retType.isScalar())
33 {
34 // No-op.
35 }
36 else if (retType.isVector())
37 {
38 size_t primarySize = retType.getNominalSize() * retType.getArraySizeProduct();
39 TIntermSequence *args = aggregateNode->getSequence();
40 size_t argsSize = 0;
41 size_t beforeSize = 0;
42 TIntermNode* lastArg = nullptr;
43 for (TIntermNode *&arg : *args)
44 {
45 TIntermTyped *targ = arg->getAsTyped();
46 lastArg = arg;
47 if (targ)
48 {
49 argsSize += targ->getNominalSize();
50 }
51 if (argsSize <= primarySize)
52 {
53 beforeSize+= targ->getNominalSize();
54 }
55 }
56 if (argsSize > primarySize)
57 {
58 size_t swizzleSize = primarySize - beforeSize;
59 TIntermTyped *targ = lastArg->getAsTyped();
60 TIntermSwizzle * newSwizzle = nullptr;
61 switch (swizzleSize)
62 {
63 case 1:
64 newSwizzle = new TIntermSwizzle(targ->deepCopy(), {0});
65 break;
66 case 2:
67 newSwizzle = new TIntermSwizzle(targ->deepCopy(), {0, 1});
68 break;
69 case 3:
70 newSwizzle = new TIntermSwizzle(targ->deepCopy(), {0, 1, 2});
71 break;
72 default:
73 // TODO(kyle): Add a comment for why this is unreachable.
74 assert(!"Should not be reached in case of 0, or 4");
75 }
76 if (newSwizzle)
77 {
78 this->queueReplacementWithParent(aggregateNode, lastArg, newSwizzle, OriginalNode::IS_DROPPED);
79 }
80 }
81 }
82 else if (retType.isMatrix())
83 {
84 // TBD if issues
85 }
86 }
87 return true;
88 }
89};
90
91} // anonymous namespace
92
93////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
94
95bool sh::FixTypeConstructors(TCompiler &compiler,
96 SymbolEnv &symbolEnv,
97 TIntermBlock &root)
98{
99 FixTypeTraverser traverser;
100 root.traverse(&traverser);
101 if (!traverser.updateTree(&compiler, &root))
102 {
103 return false;
104 }
105 return true;
106}
